    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Not a single scratch or smudge in sight\u2014it\u2019s basically a time capsule. It drives like an absolute dream and is just waiting for someone to take it on its next big adventure. If you're looking for perfection on wheels, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
