    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level 2002 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six engine with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example boasts a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M limited-slip differential. The chassis has been meticulously preserved, including proactive rear subframe reinforcement and a complete cooling system refresh. Every mechanical component, from the MacPherson strut front suspension to the multi-link rear assembly, operates with zero play, delivering the razor-sharp handling dynamics this platform is famous for. A true collector-grade vehicle with impeccable paint depth, factory-spec compression across all cylinders, and a pristine underside.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
