    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade masterpiece in showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and shows like it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no chips, swirls, or imperfections, further enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is flawless; the premium leather remains supple with no bolster wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service portfolio with every maintenance milestone performed ahead of schedule by certified technicians. Complete with all original manuals, two master keys, and a clean history, this is a rare opportunity to own a 'time capsule' example of automotive excellence.",
