      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve honestly gotta see this absolute gem in person. It\u2019s been my pride and joy and is in truly mint condition\u2014seriously, it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to get behind the wheel and love it as much as I have!",
