      "description": "Offering an exceptional 2017 Porsche 718 Cayman S in concours-level condition. This mid-engine masterpiece features the 2.5L turbocharged boxer-4 equipped with Variable Turbine Geometry (VTG), delivering linear power across the rev range. Mated to a lightning-fast 7-speed PDK dual-clutch transmission and featuring the Sport Chrono package, the mechanical synergy is unparalleled. The chassis remains factory-tight, benefiting from PASM active damping and Porsche Torque Vectoring (PTV). Every component, from the immaculate underbody to the pristine cylinder heads, reflects meticulous preventative maintenance. No track time, zero over-revs, and a flawless service history make this a turn-key collector-grade example.",
